SAMSUNG FASCINATE APP MODS
==========================

BASE VERSION: EH03

REQUIRED TOOLS: apktool

FRAMEWORKS USED IN DECOMPILE (apktool -if <framework>):
    EH03 framework-res.apk (deodexed)
    EH03 twframework-res.apk (deodexed)

FRAMEWORK-RES.APK
=================

- NOTE: Was decompiled with "apktool d --keep-broken-res"
- Enable slow-blur effect from power button popup
- Enable CRT screen off animation (nitsuj17)
- Use AOSP Gingerbread 2.3.5 battery graphics
- Change default Preference.Information layout to display 3 lines instead of 2

FRAMEWORK-RES-SBRISSENMETER.APK
===============================

- NOTE: Was decompiled with "apktool d --keep-broken-res"
- Enable slow-blur effect from power button popup
- Enable CRT screen off animation (nitsuj17)
- Use sbrissen's ED05 (Froyo) accurate battery meter and graphics
- Change default Preference.Information layout to display 3 lines instead of 2

FRAMEWORK-RES-STOCKBATTERYMETER.APK
===================================

- NOTE: Was decompiled with "apktool d --keep-broken-res"
- Enable slow-blur effect from power button popup
- Enable CRT screen off animation (nitsuj17)
- Use Stock EH03 (Froyo) battery meter and graphics
- Change default Preference.Information layout to display 3 lines instead of 2

ANDROID.POLICY.JAR
==================

- Modified for addition of Reboot and Recovery power menu options
- Stop animation services (samsungani/bootanim) at the same time

ANDROID.POLICY.JAR-PLAYER
=========================

- Modified for addition of Reboot and Recovery power menu options
- Remove Airplane Mode from power menu
- Stop animation services (samsungani/bootanim) at the same time

FRAMEWORK.JAR
=============

- Modified for addition of Reboot and Recovery power menu options
- Modified to add Settings/Sound/Charge Activation boolean option

SERVICES.JAR
============

- Changed default LiveWallpaper to com.android.wallpaper/.nexus.NexusWallpaper
- Increase default transition animation speed to 50% (Fast/0.5)
- Modified to add Settings/Sound/Charge Activation boolean option

AXT9IME.APK
===========

- Disabled key sound

BROWSER.APK
===========

- Set default home page to "about:blank"
- Remove all default bookmarks

BROWSEREH03.APK
===============

- This is the Browser from the EH03 ROM; rename to Browser.apk if using it
- Removed all default bookmarks
- Set default home page to "about:blank"
- Set default search engine to Google
- Allow all bookmarks to be deleted and/or edited
- Fix Smart URL Filter so that all search engines function (google/yahoo/bing)

CAMERA.APK
==========

- Remap power button to trigger the shutter rather than locking the controls

CARCRADLE.APK
=============

- Modified View Map to launch Google Maps instead of Bing Maps
- Modified Voice Search to use Google Voice Search instead of Bing
- Modified Navigation to launch Google Maps instead of VZNavigator

CARCRADLEEI20.APK
=================

- This is the Car Cradle from the ACG EI20 ROM; rename to CarCradle.apk if using it

DESKCRADLE.APK
==============

- Change voice search button to invoke Google Voice Search instead of Bing

DESKCRADLEEI20.APK
==================

- This is the Desk Cradle from the ACG EI20 ROM; rename to DeskCradle.apk if using it

DIALERTABACTIVITY.APK
=====================

- Modified voicemail button to dial voicemail instead of VZW Visual Voice Mail

JOBMANAGER.APK
==============

- Don't hide Google Maps, Magic Smoke Live Wallpaper or Dual Clock widget from Task Manager
- Hide many well-known launchers from Task Manager

MUSICPLAYER.APK
===============

- Localize some strings for US English
- Remove "Download from V cast?" prompt when no media exists

PHONE-PLAYER.APK
================

- Disable device activation by pretending the device is GSM

SETTINGS.APK
============

- Show full kernel version and mod/ROM version in About Phone (s0niqu3)
- Modified to add Settings/Sound/Charge Activation boolean option

SETTINGSPROVIDER.APK
====================

- Change default transition animation speed to 50% (Fast/0.5)
- Change default USB mode to "Ask on connection" (4)
- Modified to add Settings/Sound/Charge Activation boolean option
- Default airplane mode to not disable wifi (requires data wipe or a manual db edit)

SETTINGSPROVIDER-PLAYER.APK
===========================

- Change default transition animation speed to 50% (Fast/0.5)
- Change default USB mode to "Ask on connection" (4)
- Modified to add Settings/Sound/Charge Activation boolean option
- Default airplane mode to not disable wifi (requires data wipe or a manual db edit)
- Default airplane mode to ON

SYSTEMUI.APK
============

- NOTE: Was decompiled with "apktool d -r" due to problem linking back to twframework-res.apk
- (^^^^ REDO IT; add framework 2 to the yml to fix this)
- Remove full battery notification
- Remove LBS (location-based services) icon from the status bar

SYSTEMUI-PLAYER.APK
===================

- Remove full battery notification
- Remove LBS (location-based services) icon from the status bar
- Remove signal / airplane mode icon from the status bar
- Change QuickPanel Mobile Data item to Sound item (YP-G1)

TOUCHWIZ30LAUNCHER.APK
======================

- Modified default shortcut and widget layouts

TOUCHWIZ30LAUNCHEREH03.APK
==========================

- This is the TouchWiz Launcher from the EH03 ROM; rename to TouchWiz30Launcher.apk if using it
- Modified default application list order to match my ROM
- Modified default shortcut and widget layouts

TWWALLPAPERCHOOSER
==================

- Added new default wallpaper from GeeWiz ROM as a selectable item

